headline: Ralph Lauren Unveils Team USA’s Opening and Closing Ceremony Uniforms for the Milano Cortina 2026 Games
summary: NEW YORK, December 04, 2025--Ralph Lauren today unveiled Team USA’s Opening and Closing Ceremony Parade uniforms for the Olympic and Paralympic Winter Games Milano Cortina 2026.

headline: 4 Discretionary Stocks to Buy on Rising Hopes of a December Rate Cut
summary: CCL, FUBO, RL and ROKU stand out as consumer plays as firmer economic data lift sentiment and revive hopes for a December rate cut.
